ha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:18:42.000Z","msg":"可以用習近平嘅思想嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49401073c4fcf74681c81afe15acad1d20f8508e","tid":811371,"uid":199134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:20:29.000Z","msg":"給你滿滿的共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a9e54abca60a95f8436a90e8ef5f28a42833e8","tid":811371,"uid":199134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T18:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}